{{Top|leg|title=''Ubote'' group}}
'''''Ubote'' group''' was a group of three [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]]-operated [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

==History==
In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], the corvettes were ordered to [[Defense of Outpost D-34|destroy]] [[Outpost D-34]] in orbit around the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Javin]], which was located within [[Javin sector/Legends|Javin sector]]. Unfortunately for the Rebels, the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Hammer (Imperial-class)|''Hammer'']] and [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]] arrived and destroyed all three of the blockade runners before they could destroy the outpost.

